Whats the total population of Broome County?

Question 3(c)

Aggregate all bands to generate a mean NDVI raster and a maximum NDVI raster; save the two new raster datasets to the hard drive.

mean(ras)
## class       : RasterLayer 
## dimensions  : 360, 720, 259200  (nrow, ncol, ncell)
## resolution  : 0.5, 0.5  (x, y)
## extent      : -180, 180, -90, 90  (xmin, xmax, ymin, ymax)
## coord. ref. : +proj=longlat +datum=WGS84 +ellps=WGS84 +towgs84=0,0,0 
## data source : in memory
## names       : layer 
## values      : 0, 0.8537528  (min, max)
writeRaster(mean(ras),filename = "mean_ras.tif")
max(ras)
## class       : RasterLayer 
## dimensions  : 360, 720, 259200  (nrow, ncol, ncell)
## resolution  : 0.5, 0.5  (x, y)
## extent      : -180, 180, -90, 90  (xmin, xmax, ymin, ymax)
## coord. ref. : +proj=longlat +datum=WGS84 +ellps=WGS84 +towgs84=0,0,0 
## data source : in memory
## names       : layer 
## values      : 0, 0.9681  (min, max)
writeRaster(max(ras),filename = "max_ras.tif")
